STATE
v.
Kelvin L. GREENFIELD. No. 443P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 6, 2005. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, G. Dewey Hudson, District Attorney, for State.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 18th day of August 2005 by Defendant for Petition for Writ of Certiorari to review the order of the NC Court of Appeals:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 6th day of October 2005."
